<P>
   PETER-PAUL-MARY _ Now in its 38th year, Peter, Paul &AMP; Mary
remains more than a throwback to the long-haired idealism of the
'60s: It's a thriving institution. (Passy, Palm Beach Post) MOVED.
</P>
<P>
   EYMAN-ON-BOOKS _ Our critic says the decision is in: He is
America's greatest novelist, proven again with his latest, I
Married A Communist. (Eyman, Palm Beach Post) MOVED.
