<HEADER>
A9920 &Cx1f; taf-z
u w &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-ELIMINATE-CLINTON-IMP     10-27 0034
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-ELIMINATE-CLINTON-IMPEACH </SLUG>
 
<TEXT>
<P>
   EDITORS:
</P>
<P>
   CLINTON-IMPEACH (Washington) will not move in tonight's New York
Times News Service file.
</P>
