   &UR; From a newspaper contest where entrants age 4 to 15 were asked
to imitate `Deep Thoughts.' &LR;
</P>
<P>
   My young brother asked me what happens after we die. I told him
we get buried under a bunch of dirt and worms eat our bodies. I
guess I should have told him the truth--that most of us go to Hell
and burn eternally--but I didn't want to upset him. --Age 10
